text: Muhammad Sadiq Sanjrani (; born 14 April 1978) is a Pakistani politician. He is the 8th and current Chairman of the Senate of Pakistan. He took his oath of office as Member and Chairman of the Senate of Pakistan on 12 March 2018. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1978 births Category:Chairmen of the Senate of Pakistan Category:Politicians from Balochistan (Pakistan)
title: Sadiq Sanjrani
